    • parseLevel

      public static Level parseLevel(Listener listener, String text, boolean lenient)
      Parses the given value into a Level, reporting any problems to the given listener. If lenient is true, values less than 0 are resolved to zero, and levels greater than one are resolved to one.
      Parameters:
      listener - The listener
      text - The text to parse
      lenient - True to allow out-of-range values
      Returns:
      The level
